{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Animation.pause()","mdn_url":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/pause","locale":"es","native":"Español","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/Animation\"><code>Animation()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propiedades</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/currentTime\"><code>currentTime</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/effect\"><code>effect</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finished\"><code>finished</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/id\"><code>id</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/pending\"><code>pending</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playbackRate\"><code>playbackRate</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playState\"><code>playState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/ready\"><code>ready</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/replaceState\"><code>replaceState</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/startTime\"><code>startTime</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/timeline\"><code>timeline</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel\"><code>cancel()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/commitStyles\"><code>commitStyles()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish\"><code>finish()</code></a></li><li><em><code>pause()</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/persist\"><code>persist()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/play\"><code>play()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/reverse\"><code>reverse()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/updatePlaybackRate\"><code>updatePlaybackRate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eventos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel_event\"><code>cancel</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish_event\"><code>finish</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/remove_event\"><code>remove</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herencia</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a Web Animations</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationEffect\"><code>AnimationEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationPlaybackEvent\"><code>AnimationPlaybackEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationTimeline\"><code>AnimationTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/getAnimations\"><code>Document.getAnimations()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/timeline\"><code>Document.timeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentTimeline\"><code>DocumentTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Element/animate\"><code>Element.animate()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/KeyframeEffect\"><code>KeyframeEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>El método <code>pause()</code> de la interfaz <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a> de la <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Web Animations API (en-US)</a>, suspende la reproducción de la animación.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxis","title":"Sintaxis","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>animation<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">pause</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parámetros","title":"Parámetros","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Ningun.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"valor_devuelto","title":"Valor devuelto","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Ningun.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"excepciones","title":"Excepciones","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"invalidstateerror\">InvalidStateError</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>La animación <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/currentTime\" title=\"currentTime\"><code>currentTime</code></a> no está resuelta <code>unresolved</code> (por ejemplo, si nunca se ha reproducido o no se está reproduciendo actualmente) y el tiempo de finalización de la animación es infinito positivo.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>\n<p>Lanza un <code>InvalidStateError</code> si el <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/currentTime\" title=\"currentTime\"><code>currentTime</code></a> de la animación no está resuelto <code>unresolved</code> (tal vez no se haya iniciado la reproducción) y el fin de la animación es infinito positivo.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ejemplos","title":"Ejemplos","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>Animation.pause()</code> es utilizado en varias ocasiones en el juego Alice in Web Animations API Land <a href=\"https://codepen.io/rachelnabors/pen/PNYGZQ?editors=0010\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Growing/Shrinking Alice Game</a>, porque las animaciones creadas con el método <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Element/animate\"><code>Element.animate()</code></a> se inician de inmediato y deben ser detenidas manualmente para evitar esto:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// animación de la magdalena que lentamente se está comiendo</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> nommingCake <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'eat-me_sprite'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">animate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">transform</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'translateY(0)'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">transform</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'translateY(-80%)'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">fill</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'forwards'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">easing</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'steps(4, end)'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">duration</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> aliceChange<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>effect<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>timing<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>duration <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// realmente solo debe funcionar al hacer click, así que se pausa inicialmente:</span>\nnommingCake<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">pause</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Adicionalmente, al restablecer:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// Una función multiusos para pausar las animaciones de Alicia, el pastelito y la botella que dice \"drink me.\"</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">stopPlayingAlice</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  aliceChange<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">pause</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  nommingCake<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">pause</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  drinking<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">pause</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Cuando el usuario suelte el cupcake o la botella, pause las animaciones.</span>\ncake<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"mouseup\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> stopPlayingAlice<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nbottle<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"mouseup\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> stopPlayingAlice<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Especificaciones","id":"especificaciones","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/web-animations-1/#dom-animation-pause","title":"Web Animations"}],"query":"api.Animation.pause"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidad con navegadores","id":"compatibilidad_con_navegadores","isH3":false,"query":"api.Animation.pause","dataURL":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/pause/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ver_también","title":"Ver también","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Web Animations API (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a> para otros métodos y propiedades que puedes usar para el control de animaciones en páginas web.</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/pause\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>Animation.pause()</code></a> para pausar una animación.</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/reverse\"><code>Animation.reverse()</code></a> para reproducir una animación al revés.</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish\"><code>Animation.finish()</code></a> para finalizar una animación.</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel\"><code>Animation.cancel()</code></a> para cancelar una animación.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxis","id":"sintaxis"},{"text":"Ejemplos","id":"ejemplos"},{"text":"Especificaciones","id":"especificaciones"},{"text":"Compatibilidad con navegadores","id":"compatibilidad_con_navegadores"},{"text":"Ver también","id":"ver_también"}],"summary":"El método pause() de la interfaz Animation de la Web Animations API (en-US), suspende la reproducción de la animación.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Animation.pause()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"es/web/api/animation/pause","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/es/web/api/animation/pause/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/es/docs/Web","title":"Tecnología para desarrolladores web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API","title":"Referencia de la API Web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation","title":"Animation"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/pause","title":"Animation.pause()"}],"pageTitle":"Animation.pause() - Referencia de la API Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}